Speaker Nancy Pelosi has made history and shaped it by breaking glass ceilings and showing young women that there are no limits to what they can achieve. She has had a significant impact and legacy in California, Congress, and countries around the world. As the most effective Speaker in US history, her leadership and advocacy have been focused on creating an America that aligns with the ideals of the founders. She has been a strong defender of democracy, standing up for our nation's sacred ideals during difficult times. The Second Gentleman and the author wish Speaker Pelosi and her family all the best as she continues to serve California and build on her record of service in Congress.